highlights.text: Akashamayavale - From "Vellam - The Essential Drink" by Bijibal, Shahabaz Aman, and Nidheesh Naderi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kochi, up 20 spots at #65.
Sushin Shyam has the most spots on Top Songs Kochi. Athmave Poo (From "Romancham") is the highest at #1.
Aadharanjali (From "Romancham) by Sushin Shyam, Madhuvanthi Narayan, and Vinayak Sasikumar has been on Top Songs Kochi the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Vennila Chandana Kinnam - Recreated Version by Sanah Moidutty is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kochi at #86.
